# MoC (Map of Content) Structure Prompt

Generate or update a Map of Contents (MoC) note.

## MoC Data
- MoC Name: {{MOC_NAME}}
- Tags: {{TAGS}}
- Entries to Link: {{ENTRIES}}
- Concepts to Link: {{CONCEPTS}}

## OUTPUT FORMAT

Generate the full markdown file content.

Format rules:
- type: moc
- tags: always include "map-of-content" and a topic tag matching the MoC name
- Use bilingual headings: "## English / 中文"
- Body sections:
  - Overview: 1-2 sentence description of what this MoC covers
  - Entries: list of wikilinks to entry notes
  - Concepts: list of wikilinks to concept notes
  - Sources: list of wikilinks to source notes (if available)

If updating an existing MoC, preserve existing content and append new links under the appropriate section.

Output ONLY the markdown file content, no explanation.
